#: template-meaning-of-6.php:42
msgid "The Sixth Estate"
msgstr "Estet Keenam"

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:44
msgid "The Sixth Estate is what comes after the noise. It is journalism that is community-grounded rather than commercially captured. Language-first rather than language-last. Accountable to its readers rather than to its owners, its advertisers, or the government of the day. It does not wait for a press accreditation to tell the truth. It does not moderate its conclusions to preserve access to those in power."
msgstr "Estate Keenam adalah apa yang datang selepas kebisingan. Ia adalah kewartawanan yang berasaskan komuniti dan bukannya ditangkap secara komersial. Mengutamakan bahasa dan bukannya bahasa terakhir. Bertanggungjawab kepada pembacanya dan bukannya kepada pemiliknya, pengiklannya, atau kerajaan pada hari itu."

#: template-about.php:56
msgid "The UP6 editorial approach prioritises factual accuracy, contextual clarity and precise use of language. Every report is prepared from verified sources and thorough research so that readers obtain a comprehensive picture of an event or current issue. Focus is given to domestic developments in Malaysia alongside global coverage that has a direct or indirect impact on this region."
msgstr "Pendekatan editorial UP6 mengutamakan ketepatan fakta, kejelasan konteks dan penggunaan bahasa yang tepat. Setiap laporan disediakan daripada sumber yang disahkan dan penyelidikan yang teliti supaya pembaca memperoleh gambaran menyeluruh tentang sesuatu peristiwa atau isu semasa."

#: template-corrections.php:76
msgid "The URL or title of the article in question"
msgstr "URL atau tajuk artikel berkenaan"

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:69
msgid "The Urban Working Class"
msgstr "Kelas Pekerja Bandar"

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:73
msgid "The Young Malaysian"
msgstr "Orang Muda Malaysia"

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:82
msgid "The activist, the whistleblower, the academic whose research produces uncomfortable findings, the journalist who published the story that required courage — whose criticism of power is framed as disloyalty, whose motives are questioned before their evidence is examined, and who discovers that in Malaysia, what you say matters less than who it inconveniences."
msgstr "Aktivis, pemberi maklumat, ahli akademik yang penyelidikannya menghasilkan penemuan yang tidak selesa, wartawan yang menerbitkan cerita yang memerlukan keberanian — yang kritikannya terhadap kuasa dibingkai sebagai ketidaksetiaan, yang motifnya dipersoalkan sebelum buktinya diperiksa."

#: template-corrections.php:68
msgid "The affected party will be notified directly where possible"
msgstr "Pihak yang terkesan akan dimaklumkan secara langsung jika boleh"

#: 404.php:11
msgid "The article or page you were looking for could not be found."
msgstr "Artikel atau halaman yang anda cari tidak dapat ditemui."

#: template-corrections.php:70
msgid "The correction will be noted prominently rather than appended quietly"
msgstr "Pembetulan akan dicatat secara ketara dan bukan ditambah secara senyap"

#: template-editorial-policy.php:80
msgid "The date and details of updates will be recorded"
msgstr "Tarikh dan butiran kemas kini akan dicatatkan"

#: template-corrections.php:78
msgid "The evidence or source you are relying on to dispute the claim"
msgstr "Bukti atau sumber yang anda gunakan untuk mempertikaikan dakwaan tersebut"

#: template-corrections.php:94
msgid "The final decision on whether a correction is warranted rests with the senior editorial team. UP6 Suara Semasa does not accept external direction on corrections from advertisers, government bodies, or other commercial or institutional interests. Pressure to correct or retract content that is accurate will be resisted and, where appropriate, reported."
msgstr "Keputusan muktamad sama ada pembetulan diperlukan terletak pada pasukan editorial kanan. UP6 Suara Semasa tidak menerima arahan luar mengenai pembetulan daripada pengiklan, badan kerajaan, atau kepentingan komersial atau institusi lain."

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:119
msgid "The human behind every story. The person the statistic describes. The community the policy erases. The name that becomes a number in a government report. Manusia coverage is the reminder that journalism is ultimately about people — not events, not institutions, not quarterly figures — and that the measure of a report is whether the person it describes would recognise themselves in it."
msgstr "Manusia di sebalik setiap cerita. Orang yang diterangkan oleh statistik. Komuniti yang dipadamkan oleh dasar. Nama yang menjadi nombor dalam laporan kerajaan."

#: template-editorial-policy.php:96
msgid "The information provided is of significant public interest"
msgstr "Maklumat yang diberikan adalah bernilai tinggi kepada kepentingan awam"

#: template-disclaimer.php:47
msgid "The information published on UP6 Suara Semasa is provided in good faith for general informational and journalistic purposes only. While Langgam Fikir Enterprise makes every reasonable effort to ensure that content is accurate, timely, and sourced responsibly, we make no representations or warranties of any kind, express or implied, as to the completeness, accuracy, reliability, or suitability of any article, report, or other content appearing on this portal."
msgstr "Maklumat yang diterbitkan di UP6 Suara Semasa disediakan dengan niat baik untuk tujuan maklumat umum dan kewartawanan sahaja."

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:197
msgid "The name was never just a name."
msgstr "Namanya tidak pernah sekadar nama."

