#: template-about.php:83
msgid "The portal operates entirely digitally with an emphasis on fast access, high readability and consistent delivery of information to readers in Malaysia and internationally. UP6 Suara Semasa is committed to operating free of interference from any government body, law enforcement agency, regulatory authority or political entity — editorial decisions rest solely with the editorial team."
msgstr "Portal ini beroperasi sepenuhnya secara digital dengan penekanan pada akses pantas, kebolehbacaan yang tinggi dan penyampaian maklumat yang konsisten kepada pembaca di Malaysia dan antarabangsa."

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:43
msgid "The press has long been called the Fourth Estate — the informal check on the three formal branches of government. The Fifth Estate emerged with the internet: bloggers, citizen journalists, social networks that broke the monopoly of the masthead and gave the unaccredited a platform."
msgstr "Akhbar telah lama dipanggil Estate Keempat — semakan tidak rasmi terhadap tiga cabang formal kerajaan. Estate Kelima muncul dengan internet: penulis blog, wartawan rakyat, rangkaian sosial yang memecahkan monopoli masthead."

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:61
msgid "The six voices are not six named individuals. They are the six communities whose concerns too often find no reflection in the national media:"
msgstr "Enam suara itu bukan enam individu yang dinamakan. Mereka adalah enam komuniti yang kebimbangannya terlalu kerap tidak tercermin dalam media nasional:"

