#: template-about.php:42
msgid "UP6 Suara Semasa is a digital news portal focusing on coverage of current affairs in %1$s and %2$s developments, encompassing %3$s, %4$s, technology, %5$s, religion, %6$s and %7$s. The portal was established to provide timely information in %8$s with clear, organised and accessible delivery to readers of all backgrounds."
