#: template-disclaimer.php:52
msgid "UP6 Suara Semasa is a news and commentary portal, not a professional advisory service. Readers who require advice on specific personal circumstances should consult the appropriate licensed professional."
msgstr "UP6 Suara Semasa adalah portal berita dan ulasan, bukan perkhidmatan nasihat profesional."

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:90
msgid "UP6 Suara Semasa is built for all six."
