#: template-editorial-policy.php:60
msgid "UP6 Suara Semasa maintains a strict separation between editorial operations and commercial interests. Advertisers, sponsors, and owners have no authority over coverage decisions, headline selection, or article content."
msgstr "UP6 Suara Semasa mengekalkan pemisahan tegas antara operasi editorial dan kepentingan komersial."

#: template-editorial-policy.php:46
msgid "UP6 Suara Semasa operates on a commitment to accuracy, honesty, and transparency in every aspect of its reporting. This editorial policy sets out the standards applied by all journalists, editors, and contributors working under the UP6 name."
msgstr "UP6 Suara Semasa beroperasi atas komitmen kepada ketepatan, kejujuran, dan ketelusan dalam setiap aspek pelaporannya."

#: template-editorial-policy.php:94
msgid "UP6 Suara Semasa prioritises sources willing to be identified openly. Anonymous sources are accepted only when:"
