#: template-meaning-of-6.php:94
msgid "UP6 does not just cover stories. It frames them — through six distinct angles that together constitute a complete picture of the world as it affects Malaysians. Every story that arrives in our newsroom is interrogated through at least one of these lenses. Most require several."
msgstr "UP6 bukan sekadar melaporkan cerita. Ia membingkai cerita — melalui enam sudut berbeza yang bersama-sama membentuk gambaran lengkap dunia yang mempengaruhi rakyat Malaysia."

#: template-editorial-policy.php:64
msgid "UP6 endeavours to provide right of reply to all parties mentioned critically in any report. Parties approached for comment will be given reasonable time to respond before publication. If a response is not obtained, this will be explicitly stated in the article."
msgstr "UP6 berusaha untuk memberikan hak untuk menjawab kepada semua pihak yang disebut secara kritikal dalam mana-mana laporan."

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:60
msgid "UP6 exists in opposition to that narrowing. Not through confrontation for its own sake — confrontation without journalism is just noise — but through the sustained, unglamorous act of publishing: consistently, independently, in the language of the majority, what the concentrated press would rather leave unreported."
msgstr "UP6 wujud sebagai tentangan kepada penyempitan itu. Bukan melalui konfrontasi demi konfrontasi itu sendiri — konfrontasi tanpa kewartawanan hanyalah kebisingan."

#: template-editorial-policy.php:61
msgid "UP6 journalists and editors do not accept payment, gifts, or benefits from any party that may create a conflict of interest. Where a conflict of interest arises or is identified, it will be disclosed to readers or the journalist concerned will be recused from that coverage."
msgstr "Wartawan dan editor UP6 tidak menerima bayaran, hadiah, atau manfaat daripada mana-mana pihak yang boleh mewujudkan konflik kepentingan."

#: functions.php:1258
msgid "UP6 uses classic PHP templates and does not use the block-based Site Editor. Use the Customizer (here) to edit site identity, colours, menus, and footer details. To edit page content, use the standard post/page editor."
msgstr "UP6 menggunakan templat PHP klasik dan tidak menggunakan Editor Laman berasaskan blok."

#: template-meaning-of-6.php:38
msgid "UP6 was built on a different premise: that good journalism is not a single voice amplified, but multiple lenses applied — with rigour, in your language, without permission from power."
msgstr "UP6 dibina atas premis yang berbeza: bahawa kewartawanan yang baik bukan satu suara yang dikuatkan, tetapi pelbagai lensa yang digunakan."

#: template-disclaimer.php:68
msgid "Unauthorised access to or alteration of your data or transmissions"
msgstr "Akses tanpa kebenaran atau pengubahan data atau penghantaran anda"

