msgid "Uncompromised. Our editorial decisions belong to us alone — not to our advertisers, not to our owners, not to anyone who carries a badge or a portfolio."
msgstr "Tanpa kompromi. Keputusan editorial kami milik kami sahaja — bukan milik pengiklan kami, bukan milik pemilik kami."

